scenes.description: Lamy Yukihana performs her new song 'Muteki Honki da Survivor!' on stage with backup dancers.
Lamy finishes the performance and takes a pose as the audience applauds.
MC section where Lamy talks to the audience about the live performance and announces the upcoming music video release.
A sneak peek of the full animation Music Video for 'Muteki Honki da Survivor!'.
Ending message and credits with an announcement of the Music Video premiere.
